<h2>Useful tools</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.gnu.org/software/librejs/">GNU LibreJS is a free add-on for GNU IceCat and other Mozilla-based browsers.</a> It blocks nonfree nontrivial JavaScript while allowing JavaScript that is free and/or trivial.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.gnu.org/software/gnuzilla/">GNUzilla and IceCat.</a> GNUzilla is the GNU version of the Mozilla suite, and GNU IceCat is the GNU version of the Firefox browser.</li>
</ul>

